\par \pard\plain \ltrpar\s1{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\ql\rtlch\af4\afs20\lang1025\ltrch\dbch\af4\langfe255\hich\f4\fs20\lang1033\loch\f4\fs20\lang1033 {\rtlch \ltrch\loch\f4\fs24\lang1033\i0\b APPELLANTS CASE}
\par \pard\plain \ltrpar\s1\sl480\slmult1\qj{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\rtlch\af4\afs20\lang1025\ltrch\dbch\af4\langfe255\hich\f4\fs24\lang1033\loch\f4\fs24\lang1033 {\rtlch \ltrch\loch\f4\fs24\lang1033\i0\b0 Mr Subel, who appeared together with Mr Blou on behalf of the JD Group, began his argument by summarising the steps taken by the Tribunal in arriving at its decision to impose conditions on the merger:}
\par \pard\plain {\listtext\pard\plain \li720\ri0\lin720\rin0\fi-720\f4\lang1033\f4\fs24\f4\fs20\lang1025\sl480\slmult1\qj (i)\tab}\ilvl0 \ltrpar\s1\sl480\slmult1\qj{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\ls0\li720\ri0\lin720\rin0\fi-720\rtlch\af4\afs20\lang1025\ltrch\dbch\af4\langfe255\hich\f4\fs24\lang1033\loch\f4\fs24\lang1033 {\rtlch \ltrch\loch\f4\fs24\lang1033\i0\b0 Steinhoff dominated the market as defined in that it enjoyed some 54% market share.}
\par \pard\plain {\listtext\pard\plain \li720\ri0\lin720\rin0\fi-720\f4\lang1033\f4\fs24\f4\fs20\lang1025\sl480\slmult1\qj (ii)\tab}\ilvl0 \ltrpar\s1\sl480\slmult1\qj{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\ls0\li720\ri0\lin720\rin0\fi-720\rtlch\af4\afs20\lang1025\ltrch\dbch\af4\langfe255\hich\f4\fs24\lang1033\loch\f4\fs24\lang1033 {\rtlch \ltrch\loch\f4\fs24\lang1033\i0\b0 Steinhoff enjoyed an extremely close business relationship with the JD Group.}
\par \pard\plain {\listtext\pard\plain \li720\ri0\lin720\rin0\fi-720\f4\lang1033\f4\fs24\f4\fs20\lang1025\sl480\slmult1\qj (iii)\tab}\ilvl0 \ltrpar\s1\sl480\slmult1\qj{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\ls0\li720\ri0\lin720\rin0\fi-720\rtlch\af4\afs20\lang1025\ltrch\dbch\af4\langfe255\hich\f4\fs24\lang1033\loch\f4\fs24\lang1033 {\rtlch \ltrch\loch\f4\fs24\lang1033\i0\b0 Because of the merger, business would be diverted by Profurn to Steinhoff from the independent manufacturers which would only increase the market share of Steinhoff.  This would result in increased prices charged to competitors, a reduction in the choice o
f goods available on the market and hence an increase in the barrier for entry in both vertical and horizontal markets.}
\par \pard\plain \ltrpar\s1\sl480\slmult1\qj{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\rtlch\af4\afs20\lang1025\ltrch\dbch\af4\langfe255\hich\f4\fs24\lang1033\loch\f4\fs24\lang1033 
